{"nodes": [{"id": "2026_06_09_typed_action_registry_keybindings_design_document", "label": "Design", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-09-typed-action-registry-keybindings/design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "2026_06_09_typed_action_registry_keybindings_design_context", "label": "Context", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-09-typed-action-registry-keybindings/design.md", "source_location": "line 1", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "pi-vimmode already has three foundations this change should reuse: - Semantic keymap config in `src/config.ts` / `src/types.ts` for operators, motions, commands, macros, marks, text objects, and operator motions."}, {"id": "2026_06_09_typed_action_registry_keybindings_design_goals_non_goals", "label": "Goals / Non-Goals", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-09-typed-action-registry-keybindings/design.md", "source_location": "line 13", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "**Goals:** - Add canonical bindable prompt transform action IDs: `prompt.transform.quote`, `prompt.transform.unquote`, `prompt.transform.bulletize`, `prompt.transform.fence`, `prompt.transform.indent`, `prompt.transform.dedent`, `prompt.transform.reflow`."}, {"id": "2026_06_09_typed_action_registry_keybindings_design_decisions", "label": "Decisions", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-09-typed-action-registry-keybindings/design.md", "source_location": "line 37", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "### Decision 1: Registry is prompt-transform-first Add `src/prompt-transform-actions.ts` with prompt transform action metadata and shared validation. The registry describes actions and normalizes args; it does not execute prompt edits. `src/customization.ts` remains the diagnostic formatter and protected-shortcut explanation seam, importing prompt transform action metadata from `src/prompt-transform-actions.ts`. Do not migrate command/motion/operator metadata in this change."}, {"id": "2026_06_09_typed_action_registry_keybindings_design_decision_1_registry_is_prompt_transform_first", "label": "Decision 1: Registry is prompt-transform-first", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-09-typed-action-registry-keybindings/design.md", "source_location": "line 39", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Add `src/prompt-transform-actions.ts` with prompt transform action metadata and shared validation. The registry describes actions and normalizes args; it does not execute prompt edits. `src/customization.ts` remains the diagnostic formatter and protected-shortcut explanation seam, importing prompt transform action metadata from `src/prompt-transform-actions.ts`. Do not migrate command/motion/operator metadata in this change. Rejected alternatives:"}, {"id": "2026_06_09_typed_action_registry_keybindings_design_decision_2_bindable_ids_are_separate_from_all_registry_ids", "label": "Decision 2: Bindable IDs are separate from all registry IDs", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-09-typed-action-registry-keybindings/design.md", "source_location": "line 48", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Define a canonical bindable prompt transform action ID type for config-bindable prompt transforms. Keep the existing short-name `PromptTransformAction` union for transform internals and Ex command aliases. Sketch:"}, {"id": "2026_06_09_typed_action_registry_keybindings_design_decision_3_resolved_action_bindings_carry_per_key_args", "label": "Decision 3: Resolved action bindings carry per-key args", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-09-typed-action-registry-keybindings/design.md", "source_location": "line 70", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Existing keymap groups store `Record<id, string[]>`, but action bindings can attach args per key. User config uses flat canonical action IDs mapped to arrays whose entries are either a key string or an object `{ key, args }`. ```json"}, {"id": "2026_06_09_typed_action_registry_keybindings_design_decision_4_config_resolution_filters_action_bindings", "label": "Decision 4: Config resolution filters action bindings", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-09-typed-action-registry-keybindings/design.md", "source_location": "line 112", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Add action parsing helpers instead of expanding `parseKeymap(...)` inline: ```txt"}, {"id": "2026_06_09_typed_action_registry_keybindings_design_decision_5_src_commands_ts_remains_modal_grammar_source_of_truth", "label": "Decision 5: src/commands.ts remains modal grammar source of truth", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-09-typed-action-registry-keybindings/design.md", "source_location": "line 141", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Add an action binding result to `SemanticCommandResult` and include accepted action bindings in the existing binding lookup path. Counts, prefixes, and pending state continue flowing through `resolveNormalCommand(...)`. ```txt"}, {"id": "2026_06_09_typed_action_registry_keybindings_design_decision_6_shared_transform_arg_validation_normalizes_invocation_specific_syntax", "label": "Decision 6: Shared transform arg validation normalizes invocation-specific syntax", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-09-typed-action-registry-keybindings/design.md", "source_location": "line 160", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Ex transform args are positional strings. Keymap action args are objects. `src/prompt-transform-actions.ts` should expose helpers that normalize both forms into the same `PromptTransform` shape. Example shape:"}, {"id": "2026_06_09_typed_action_registry_keybindings_design_decision_7_modal_dispatch_reuses_existing_transform_helpers_and_preserves_side_effects", "label": "Decision 7: Modal dispatch reuses existing transform helpers and preserves side effects", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-09-typed-action-registry-keybindings/design.md", "source_location": "line 179", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Action dispatch in normal/visual modes computes a line range and calls `applyPromptTransform(...)`. Range rules:"}, {"id": "2026_06_09_typed_action_registry_keybindings_design_ref_src_config_ts", "label": "config.ts", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-09-typed-action-registry-keybindings/design.md", "source_location": "line 5", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "2026_06_09_typed_action_registry_keybindings_design_ref_src_types_ts", "label": "types.ts", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-09-typed-action-registry-keybindings/design.md", "source_location": "line 5", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "2026_06_09_typed_action_registry_keybindings_design_ref_src_commands_ts", "label": "commands.ts", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "openspec/changes/archive/2026-06-09-typed-action-registry-keybindings/design.md", "source_location": "line 6", "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor"